China admin code → province, grid, and electricity price

cn_admin_data.Rd

Provincial/municipal administrative codes mapped to province name, grid operator label, and residential electricity price (RMB per kWh, tax included).

Usage

cn_admin_data

Format

A tibble/data frame with N rows and 4 variables:

AdminCode

integer. GB/T admin code at provincial level.

Province

character. Province/autonomous region/municipality name.

GridName

character. Grid operator label used to select emission factors.

ElecPrice_RMB_per_kWh

numeric. Electricity price (RMB/kWh, VAT included).

Examples

head(cn_admin_data)
#> # A tibble: 6 × 4
#>   AdminCode Province     GridName                 ElecPrice_RMB_per_kWh
#>       <dbl> <chr>        <chr>                                    <dbl>
#> 1    110000 北京市       Electricity_华北电网公司                 0.488
#> 2    120000 天津市       Electricity_华北电网公司                 0.49 
#> 3    130000 河北省       Electricity_华北电网公司                 0.52 
#> 4    140000 山西省       Electricity_华北电网公司                 0.477
#> 5    150000 内蒙古自治区 Electricity_华北电网公司                 0.415
#> 6    210000 辽宁省       Electricity_中国东北电网                 0.5
